data.description: Endless possibilities and tremendous convenience makes this property most desirable! Add another unit in the back, turn 3 units into 4 units, and enjoy great cash flow. 2 minutes to 580 freeway, 20 minutes to San Francisco, less than 5 minutes to downtown Oakland, ideally and centrally located 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 1150 sqft, newly painted apartments with inside washer and dryer that makes life extremely convenient. Close to Piedmont Ave with access to a plethora of restaurants, entertainment, shopping, and high rated Oakland Technical High School. Live your best life in this fabulous property or proudly add it to your investment portfolio for the long term. Plenty of upside. Don’t miss out on this extremely rare opportunity!
